title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 164] Synth, New Wave
description:
I can't believe it's been over a year since I posted the last instalment of this extensive archive of lesser known or 
hard to find 80's record. Throughout the series I have tried to diversify what I post so that it could offer downloaders with different musical tastes something to discover & enjoy. So here's part 164 for those into synthpop.

Download a torrent? seed a torrent! & let it be out there for the others to find these as well. Love to all!

Sherrie Actor - American Solitaire [1982]
Small Affairs - Small Affairs (1985)
T-4-2 - Shockra [1984]
Walk The Walk - Walk The Walk (1986)
